column2: which can be matched against values in segim

column1: # xmax     -  x position of maximum flux
# ymax     -  y position of maximum flux
# RAmax    -  Right Ascension of max flux
# z        -  Redshift. Only robust for QOP=3
# R50_it   -  Approximate elliptical semi-major axis containing 50% of the flux (arcsec)
# R90_it   -  Approximate elliptical semi-major axis containing 90% of the flux (arcsec)
# axrat_it -  Axial ratio as given by min/maj
# ang_it   -  Orientation of the semi-major axis (cc from Y axis)
